# [[administration]]; the process or practice of managing.

# [[resolution]]; the adaptive resolution of evolving complexity and chaos in science, society, and perception into a dynamic system of controlled order. (paraphrased and expanded from the definition in the 1963 Reinhold Encyclopedia of Management, now out of print). [[User:Roebuckr|Roebuckr]] 20:21, 12 May 2006 (UTC)

